      </h2>

      <p class="text-[#000000] opacity-80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If your trusted circle misses the alert, Eyegle escalates with trained
        support and emergency coordination when needed.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[#CC0000] text-sm italic">
        Only available for Indian Users currently
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Image -->
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
      <Image
        src={BackupImage}
        alt="Backup Image"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover md:rounded-r-2xl"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
